    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a general perceived attribute of an object or light resulting from the response of vision to the wavelength of reflected or transmitted light. The principal dimensions of color when discussing painting are the variables or attributes of hue, tone, and intensity. When referring to individual chromatic colors and achromatic colors or neutrals, use "colors (hues or tints)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046343/Clugston, New Penguin Dictionary of Science (1998)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para referirse a las cualidades percibidas que resultan de la respuesta de la visión a la longitud de onda de la luz reflejada o transmitida. Para los colores cromáticos individuales o neutros, use "color”.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Waargenomen eigenschappen die het resultaat zijn van het reageren van de visuele zintuigen op de golflengte van weerkaatst of overgebracht licht. De belangrijkste kleurdimensies zijn de variabelen of kenmerken kleurschakering, tint en intensiteit. Zie 'kleuren' voor afzonderlijke chromatische kleuren en achromatische kleuren of neutrale kleuren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指對某物體或光線的一般知覺屬性，源自視覺對反射或傳送之光線波長產生的反應。在討論繪畫時，顏色的主要度量面向為色相、色調，以及彩度的變化或特質。個別論及有彩顏色、無彩顏色或中性顏色時，則使用「色彩（色相或顏色）」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refere-se a um atributo geral percebido de um objeto ou luz resultante da resposta da visão ao comprimento de onda da luz refletida ou transmitida. As principais dimensões da cor ao discutir pintura são as variáveis ​​ou atributos de matiz, tom e intensidade. Ao se referir a cores cromáticas individuais e cores acromáticas ou neutras, use "cores (ou matizes)</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
